{"tid":2338902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港人申請澳洲新永居簽證　豁免技術簽證一般條件","createTime":"2020-12-24T09:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T03:37:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e698b38b66f33cf0294e4d500184dbbc09bea2","tid":2338902,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"本台記者10月23日參加了網上舉行的總理多元文化論壇，希望親身向圖治查詢，惟當日未獲安排發問。<br />\n<br />\n內政部發言人今日回覆本台表示，當日因問題眾多，總理及部長未有一一解答。<br />\n<br />\n不過，發言人進一步透露了申請永居簽證的條件。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「這款永久居留簽證仍在制訂，但合資格的香港護照持有人，將不需要符合其他技術簽證通常要求的額外條件（eligible Hong Kong passport holders will not be required to meet the additional criteria typically required for other skilled visas.）。」<br />\n<br />\n發言人續道：「永久居留簽證選項的更多細節，將在2021年初公佈。」<br />\n<br />\n內政部較早前向本台表示，申請臨時簽證時，須持有香港特區護照才符合延長5年簽證及之後申請永居簽證的資格，若只持有英國國民（海外）護照，則不合資格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/exclusive-good-news-for-hong-kongers-looking-to-apply-for-new-permanent-visa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fexclusive-good-news-for-hong-kongers-looking-to-apply-for-new-permanent-visa&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=9681e821\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/exclusive-good-news-for-hong-kongers-looking-to-apply-for-new-permanent-visa</a>"},{"pid":"96632afd597ee208df224c0c69c9c09b91a46f68","tid":2338902,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"支那「港人」呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb410621e6e97d472fb040a5b2b5b7f1df33258","tid":2338902,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:44:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1404c35a1848b9e7dbaab3ef58ed6cd336ffdccb","